title: Ga Tech beats Florida State on 78-yard return on final play
text:
> Georgia Ga Tech beats Florida State on 78-yard return on final play Fans celebrate after Georgia Tech beat Florida State in an NCAA college football game, Saturday, Oct. 24, 2015, in Atlanta. Georgia Tech won 22-16.
